item.title: fly
item.description: Hi, I’m fly, and this is my blog! 🐱‍🐉 I like challenging things (sometimes) 🐱‍💻 I study Computer Science @TUM 🐱‍👤 I’m learning Python, Lua, Java, Javascript, C, OCaml, x86 ASM 🐱‍🏍 I love problem solving and programming - but most importantly: I love cats! If that doesn’t sound like me, you’re probably have the wrong person!
